overview: Look up “Big tits” in the dictionary--chances are you'll find a picture of Kitten Natividad and her world-class mammaries. Look in Volume 11 of Bobby Hollander's Breast Worx and you'll see the definitive queen of ‘titillation’ doing the deed…bigtime! Kitten and bosom buddy, Lee Carroll, let 'em all hang out for an unbridled girl/girl session before calling on up and coming super-stud Tanner to do mop-up honors. They're in for a hot, humongous, hooter- humping by Tanner's tail-thumping throb thruster! And, as if that isn't enough… Jim and Dee Dee proceed to pull out all the stops for a grand finale that will have you standing with a big, one gun salute. It's hard… to beat it.
title: Breast Worx 11
